This paper is about developing a conversational agent that can communicate engagingly with personality and empathy, ask and answer questions, discuss topics and situations, and perceive and converse about images. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-categories of Natural Language Processing (cs.CL), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Machine Learning (cs.LG). Additionally, since the paper deals with image perception and conversation, it may also belong to the sub-categories of Computer Vision (cs.CV) and Information Retrieval (cs.IR).
